Package: discordr
Title: Send Messages and Files to Discord from R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicklas", "Bryder", , "Nicklas.Bryder@gmail.com", role = "cre")
Description: Provides functions to send messages, embeds, and files to Discord 
    webhooks directly from R. Useful for monitoring long-running analyses, 
    sending notifications, and sharing results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
